tools.description:
Query the current position and environment of a specified agent.

Args:
    agent_id (str): The unique identifier of the agent.

Returns:
    dict: {
        "success": True,
        "data": {
            "position": str,
            "environment_id": str
        }
    }
    OR
    {
        "success": False,
        "error": str  # If agent_id does not exist.
    }

Constraints:
    - agent_id must exist in the environment.
